[TITLE]
Rule premises on SYSTEM CLOCKTIME and SYSTEM TIME (writer must emit H:MM:SS)

[JUNCTIONS]
J1    0    50

[RESERVOIRS]
R1    0

[PIPES]
P1    R1    J1    1000    12    100    0    Open

[PUMPS]
PMP1    R1    J1    HEAD C1

[CURVES]
C1    0       300
C1    1000    200

[RULES]
RULE 1
IF SYSTEM CLOCKTIME >= 6:30:00
AND SYSTEM CLOCKTIME < 22:00
THEN LINK PMP1 STATUS IS OPEN
PRIORITY 2

RULE 2
IF SYSTEM TIME > 2:00
THEN LINK PMP1 STATUS IS CLOSED
PRIORITY 1

[OPTIONS]
Units    GPM
Headloss    H-W

[TIMES]
Duration    24:00
Hydraulic Timestep    1:00
Report Timestep    1:00
Start Clocktime    12 AM

[END]
